{
  "stem": "25348.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went there for a few days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they didn't tell me where I was going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was thinking I might be left here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's no one to advise me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you-- you dare not ask.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thought I was going to Germany, where nobody would know me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my hope almost died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm ashamed to say it, but I'll tell you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There came a Jew with a nose like this, whose language at home was not Polish, who asked me in a very poor Polish-- he was-- he was flanked by two SS men.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came to seek out the remnants of Jewry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They helped someone escape to that camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said to me, aren't you too young to be here?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was paralyzed with fear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't answer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] For a while, he stood there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the SS men, ready to pounce.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I tell you things a little-- a little bit drawn out at times.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you might think they're trivial.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when I told you I peeled potatoes, it wasn't a solo job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some peasants there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they spoke, amongst themselves, a dialect which as a kid, I picked up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is very hard to translate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because when you speak Polish, you'd know that it's a peasant dialect.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't know what to tell this man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And suddenly, like an arrow came through my head.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I answered him in this dialect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No Jew speaks like this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Had I had I a cannon full of bullets, he wouldn't be running as fast.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was ashamed, approaching a-- a peasant offspring, suspecting to be a Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was ashamed in front of these SS men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
